translated: Johanson, Erik, director, Traniås, b. 16/7/84 in Tranås to grocer Jonas J. and Emma Fälth. Married 11 years to Brita Noird-ling. Children: Iniga-Brita b. 12, Anina-Gneta b. 13 - Jönköping, living in first marriage. Studied at Pahltoans hand:inst., language and trade school, and various positions in Hamburg, London, and Paris 04-07. Partial owner in 08 of the company established by father in 75, which was restructured in 16 to A-B Johanson & Son, formed 19 J. Johanson's A-B, director in both companies until 42. Former member of city council's preparation committee, former chairman of the health committee, member of the church council, public school board, and cemetery committee, chairman of the Tranås merchant association 24-44, now honorary chairman, honorary member of the Jönköping merchant association.
